Title: Microsoft Testing Platform is cool!
Description: I love xUnit and I use it for most of my testing. With xUnit v3 the possibility of running the tests was added without the need of using any other external tools like console runners, dotnet test or VSTest. So a xUnit test suite is just a executable itself. Not long after xUnit v3 were released I discovered Microsoft Testing Platform, which achieves something very similar. According to their own docs it “[..]is a lightweight and portable alternative to VSTest for running tests in all contexts”.
